# isort / pre-commit transient artifacts.
# These are written+renamed in-place while formatting and can be picked up
# mid-write by CDK SOURCE asset fingerprinting (TOCTOU -> ENOENT on *.isorted).
# NOTE: .gitignore does NOT affect CDK fingerprinting; the real fix is to not
# run isort/pre-commit concurrently with `cdk deploy`/`cdk synth`.
*.isorted


# zip fikes
*.zip
!medialake_constructs/shared_constructs/*.zip


# lambda temp files
**/package/

## aws-exports.json
aws-exports.json
config.json
config.json.bkp
